article.story: BIRMINGHAM, Ala. -- — Achor Achor had 21 points in Samford's 92-80 win over Citadel on Saturday night. Achor was 7-of-12 shooting and 7 of 7 from the free-throw line for the Bulldogs (26-5, 15-3 Southern Conference). Nathan Johnson shot 4 for 7 (3 for 6 from 3-point range) and 7 of 10 from the free-throw line to add 18 points. Dallas Graziani had 11 points and was 4-of-6 shooting (3 for 5 from 3-point range). Quentin Millora-Brown finished with 16 points and 11 rebounds for the Bulldogs (11-20, 3-15). AJ Smith added 15 points for Citadel. Colby McAllister also put up 14 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
